---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog — 阅读与思考
description: 专注阅读与思考的博客 — 技术、设计与生活随笔。
---

<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">
      阅读与思考
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-xl mb-2">
      记录开发、产品和生活中的思考，慢慢打磨自己的作品和想法。
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">
      当前共 <span class="font-semibold text-zinc-300">{{ collections.posts | length }}</span> 篇文章。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="posts" class="mb-16" aria-labelledby="posts-heading">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mb-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
      <h2 id="posts-heading" class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">文章</h2>
      <div class="w-full md:w-72">
        <label for="post-search" class="sr-only">搜索文章</label>
        <input
          id="post-search"
          type="search"
          placeholder="按标题或日期搜索，例如 2025-02-08"
          class="w-full rounded-lg border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-100 placeholder-zinc-500 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500/30 outline-none transition-all duration-200"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article
        class="group rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-800/50 p-5 cursor-pointer hover:border-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all duration-200 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-blue-500 focus-within:ring-offset-2 focus-within:ring-offset-[#18181b]"
        data-title="{{ post.data.title | lower }}"
        data-date="{{ post.data.date | dateFmt }}"
      >
        <a href="{{ baseUrl }}{{ post.url }}" class="block">
          <time class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-2 block" datetime="{{ post.data.date | dateFmt }}">{{ post.data.date | dateFmt }}</time>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200 line-clamp-2">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 line-clamp-2">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-800/30 p-6 md:p-8" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
    <h2 id="about-heading" class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">关于作者</h2>
    <div class="flex gap-6">
      <div class="h-16 w-16 shrink-0 rounded-xl bg-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-2">
          candy，独立开发者，喜欢把想法变成可以被真正使用的产品。
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          这个博客主要记录开发实践、产品思考和一些个人观察，希望对后来看到的人也有一点点帮助。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<script>
  (function () {
    var input = document.getElementById('post-search');
    if (!input) return;
    var cards = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-title][data-date]'));

    input.addEventListener('input', function () {
      var q = this.value.trim().toLowerCase();
      cards.forEach(function (card) {
        var title = card.dataset.title || '';
        var date = (card.dataset.date || '').toLowerCase();
        var match = !q || title.indexOf(q) !== -1 || date.indexOf(q) !== -1;
        card.classList.toggle('hidden', !match);
        card.setAttribute('aria-hidden', match ? 'false' : 'true');
      });
    });
  })();
</script>
